1
00:00:39,659 --> 00:00:45,259
<b>01 Underworld - Unrated Extended
Action 2003 [H264-mp4] English</b>

2
00:00:50,960 --> 00:00:53,339
[ THUNDER CRASHES ]

3
00:00:59,050 --> 00:01:03,179
[ WOMAN ] The war had all but ground
to a halt in the blink of an eye.

4
00:01:05,270 --> 00:01:12,359
Lucian, the most feared and ruthless leader ever
to rule the Lycan clan had finally been killed.

5
00:01:14,940 --> 00:01:20,489
The Lycan horde scattered to the wind in a
single evening of flame and retribution.

6
00:01:24,770 --> 00:01:27,689
Victory, it seemed, was in our grasp,

7
00:01:27,790 --> 00:01:30,829
the very birthright of the Vampires.

8
00:01:35,420 --> 00:01:38,489
Nearly six centuries had
passed since that night.

9
00:01:38,760 --> 00:01:43,509
Yet the ancient blood feud proved
unwilling to follow Lucian to the grave.

10
00:01:44,260 --> 00:01:46,599
Though Lycans were fewer in number,

11
00:01:46,600 --> 00:01:49,099
the war itself had become more perilous

12
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:52,649
for the moon no longer held her sway.

13
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:58,359
Older, more powerful Lycans
were now able to change at will.

14
00:01:58,990 --> 00:02:02,819
The weapons had evolved,
but our orders remained the same:

15
00:02:02,820 --> 00:02:06,779
Hunt them down and kill them off,
one by one.

16
00:02:07,950 --> 00:02:10,369
A most successful campaign.

17
00:02:10,370 --> 00:02:13,959
Perhaps too successful.

18
00:02:24,510 --> 00:02:27,389
For those like me, a Death Dealer,

19
00:02:27,390 --> 00:02:30,139
this signalled the end of an era.

20
00:02:30,810 --> 00:02:35,809
Like the weapons of the previous
century, we too would become obsolete.

21
00:02:35,810 --> 00:02:39,359
Pity, because I lived for it.

22
00:04:03,070 --> 00:04:05,319
[ MAN 1 GRUNTS ] [ MAN 2 ] Hey!

23
00:04:24,630 --> 00:04:26,519
Bloods...

24
00:04:27,930 --> 00:04:30,259
[ PEOPLE SCREAMING ]

25
00:05:24,570 --> 00:05:25,779
[ SCREAMS ]

26
00:05:49,220 --> 00:05:52,259
It's all right. It's all right.
You're going to be okay.

27
00:07:06,750 --> 00:07:09,459
[ GRUNTING ]

28
00:07:20,220 --> 00:07:21,419
[ GROWLING ]

29
00:07:55,590 --> 00:07:57,129
[ LYCAN ROARS IN DISTANCE ]

30
00:08:52,980 --> 00:08:54,059
[ YELLING ]

31
00:08:58,820 --> 00:09:01,199
[ BELL TOLLING ]

32
00:09:22,300 --> 00:09:23,549
[ LYCAN GROWLS ]

33
00:10:02,930 --> 00:10:04,770
[ LYCANS GROWLING ]
[ MEN YELLING IN DISTANCE ]

34
00:10:48,140 --> 00:10:49,349
[ YELLING INDISTINCTLY ]

35
00:10:59,980 --> 00:11:01,149
[ YELLING SILENCES ]

36
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:26,089
You're acting like a pack of rabid dogs!

37
00:11:27,470 --> 00:11:30,389
And that, gentlemen,

38
00:11:30,390 --> 00:11:32,429
simply will not do.

39
00:11:32,430 --> 00:11:36,849
Not if you expect to defeat
the Vampires on their own ground.

40
00:11:37,730 --> 00:11:41,439
Not if you expect to survive at all.

41
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:44,449
- Pierce!
- Taylor!

42
00:11:46,450 --> 00:11:48,069
Put some clothes on, will you?

43
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:04,129
[ DEVICE BEEPS ]

44
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:30,819
We have a serious problem.

45
00:12:46,220 --> 00:12:47,929
I will have to run a few tests.

46
00:12:47,930 --> 00:12:52,759
It's definitely an irradiated fluid
of some sort. Ultraviolet ammunition.

47
00:12:53,260 --> 00:12:55,059
Daylight, harnessed as a weapon.

48
00:12:55,480 --> 00:12:57,939
You expect me to believe
that a mangy animal

49
00:12:58,390 --> 00:13:01,479
came up with a bullet specifically
engineered to kill Vampires?

50
00:13:01,480 --> 00:13:03,439
No, I am betting it's military.

51
00:13:03,860 --> 00:13:06,899
Something they stole.
Some sort of high-tech tracer round.

52
00:13:06,900 --> 00:13:09,199
Look,
I don't care where they got these things.

53
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:12,279
Rigel is dead, and Nathaniel
could still be out there.

54
00:13:12,280 --> 00:13:14,659
We should gather the Death Dealers
and head back down there in force.

55
00:13:14,660 --> 00:13:17,789
Absolutely not. Not now.
Not for a random incursion.

56
00:13:17,790 --> 00:13:22,259
The Awakening is a few days off, and this
house is in state of unrest as it is.

57
00:13:22,260 --> 00:13:25,589
Random? They opened fire on us
in full view of the public.

58
00:13:25,590 --> 00:13:27,579
And from the commotion I heard
down in that tunnel...

59
00:13:27,580 --> 00:13:30,269
You said yourself
you didn't actually see anything.

60
00:13:30,800 --> 00:13:33,299
Look, I know what I heard,
and I know what my gut tells me,

61
00:13:33,300 --> 00:13:36,719
and I am telling you there could be
dozens of Lycans down there.

62
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:38,809
Who knows, maybe more. Hundreds.

63
00:13:39,100 --> 00:13:41,649
We have hunted them
to the brink of extinction.

64
00:13:43,400 --> 00:13:45,109
Kraven's right, Selene.

65
00:13:45,110 --> 00:13:49,359
There's not been a den of that magnitude for
centuries, not since the days of Lucian.

66
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:51,199
I know that, Kahn.

67
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:54,159
But I'd rather have you prove
me wrong by checking it out.

68
00:13:55,830 --> 00:13:57,659
Very well,
have your men tighten things up.

69
00:13:57,660 --> 00:13:59,999
I will have Soren assemble a search team.

70
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:01,919
No, I want to lead the team myself.

71
00:14:01,920 --> 00:14:05,539
Absolutely not!
Soren will handle it.

72
00:14:06,340 --> 00:14:08,549
Hundreds, really?

73
00:14:09,170 --> 00:14:10,549
Viktor would believe me.

74
00:14:15,640 --> 00:14:17,179
I'd never dream of treating you like that.

75
00:14:17,180 --> 00:14:18,389
Of course you wouldn't.

76
00:14:18,810 --> 00:14:23,849
Now run along and make sure she's dressed
and ready for the arrival of her guests.

77
00:15:33,220 --> 00:15:34,679
It's a waste of time, you know.

78
00:15:34,680 --> 00:15:36,259
What is?

79
00:15:36,260 --> 00:15:38,759
Well, I seriously doubt Viktor would
want you freezing to death in here,

80
00:15:38,760 --> 00:15:40,559
staring at his tomb for hours on end.

81
00:15:40,560 --> 00:15:45,389
No, he'd want the Death Dealers out there
right now, scouring every inch of the city.

82
00:15:45,390 --> 00:15:49,939
Kraven. I will never understand
why Viktor left him in charge.

83
00:15:49,940 --> 00:15:52,529
He's a bureaucrat, not a warrior.

84
00:15:53,780 --> 00:15:55,069
Come on, we need to get you ready.

85
00:15:55,070 --> 00:15:56,239
For what?

86
00:15:56,240 --> 00:15:57,529
The party.

87
00:15:57,530 --> 00:16:00,409
Amelia's envoy will be here any minute.

88
00:16:57,970 --> 00:17:00,089
Oh, yes.

89
00:17:00,090 --> 00:17:02,509
You should definitely wear this one.
It's perfect.

90
00:17:29,250 --> 00:17:30,959
They were after you.

91
00:17:38,470 --> 00:17:40,219
He's attractive.

92
00:17:40,220 --> 00:17:41,379
For a human.

93
00:17:41,380 --> 00:17:42,799
[ KRAVEN ] Who's attractive?

94
00:17:56,730 --> 00:17:59,149
You know I was planning to have you
at my side this evening.

95
00:17:59,150 --> 00:18:01,739
Take Erika.
She's dying to be at your side.

96
00:18:04,580 --> 00:18:09,119
If you ask me, you take this warrior
business far too seriously.

97
00:18:10,540 --> 00:18:14,749
You can't undo the past,
no matter how many you kill.

98
00:18:15,250 --> 00:18:17,169
And besides...

99
00:18:17,760 --> 00:18:19,799
what's the point in being immortal

100
00:18:19,800 --> 00:18:22,469
if you deny yourself
the simple pleasures in life?

101
00:18:22,470 --> 00:18:24,929
Do you see this human? [ SIGHS ]

102
00:18:24,930 --> 00:18:26,179
What of him?

103
00:18:26,180 --> 00:18:30,269
I can't be positive, but I am beginning
to think the Lycans of... Blast.

104
00:18:35,400 --> 00:18:38,019
Put on something elegant
and be quick about it.

105
00:18:38,020 --> 00:18:41,609
Kraven, I am serious.
I think they were following him.

106
00:18:44,200 --> 00:18:47,489
Other than food,
why would Lycans stalk a human?

107
00:19:45,180 --> 00:19:46,969
[ YELLS ]

108
00:20:01,110 --> 00:20:02,569
Any progress?

109
00:20:02,570 --> 00:20:05,239
Let's find out.

110
00:20:12,950 --> 00:20:15,039
Negative.

111
00:20:30,550 --> 00:20:32,219
You heading home?

112
00:20:33,390 --> 00:20:36,099
Yeah, Nicholas gave me a couple hours off.

113
00:20:36,480 --> 00:20:41,559
By the way he said you did a terrific job
tonight with the surgery.

114
00:20:41,560 --> 00:20:43,189
Yeah.

115
00:20:46,280 --> 00:20:47,899
Take it easy.

116
00:21:43,630 --> 00:21:45,499
We were ambushed.

117
00:21:45,800 --> 00:21:47,509
Death Dealers, three of them.

118
00:21:47,510 --> 00:21:49,219
And the candidate?

119
00:21:49,220 --> 00:21:51,339
We lost him. You lost him.

120
00:21:53,600 --> 00:21:55,179
Look at this mess.

121
00:21:55,390 --> 00:21:58,139
Ag rounds. High content.

122
00:21:58,140 --> 00:22:00,389
Prevented him from making the change.

123
00:22:05,730 --> 00:22:09,279
No use in digging out the rest.
Silver's penetrated his organs.

124
00:22:09,280 --> 00:22:12,029
Regeneration's impossible at this point.

125
00:22:14,620 --> 00:22:16,699
Let's take these out.

126
00:22:21,040 --> 00:22:22,749
Relax.

127
00:22:25,590 --> 00:22:26,590
[ GRUNTS ]

128
00:22:28,050 --> 00:22:32,679
The Vampires didn't realize
you were following a human.

129
00:22:32,680 --> 00:22:35,089
- Did they, Raze?
- No.

130
00:22:35,680 --> 00:22:36,679
[ GRUNTS ]

131
00:22:36,680 --> 00:22:37,929
I mean...

132
00:22:37,930 --> 00:22:39,809
I don't think so.

133
00:22:39,810 --> 00:22:41,729
You don't think, or you don't know?

134
00:22:42,440 --> 00:22:43,729
I am not sure.

135
00:22:43,730 --> 00:22:44,899
[ GRUNTS ]

136
00:23:01,290 --> 00:23:02,959
Negative.

137
00:23:04,630 --> 00:23:06,789
I really must have a look at this Michael.

138
00:23:08,380 --> 00:23:10,549
Must I do everything myself?

139
00:23:21,810 --> 00:23:27,359
Our noble houses may be
separated by a great ocean,

140
00:23:27,360 --> 00:23:32,569
but we are equally committed
to the survival of the bloodlines.

141
00:23:32,570 --> 00:23:35,739
And when Amelia arrives to awaken Marcus

142
00:23:35,740 --> 00:23:38,989
in just two days' time,

143
00:23:39,410 --> 00:23:43,079
we shall once again
be united as a single coven!

144
00:23:43,080 --> 00:23:45,119
[ ALL CHATTER ]

145
00:23:47,670 --> 00:23:52,379
[ MAN ] We want to thank our hosts
for their generous hospitality.

146
00:23:57,430 --> 00:23:59,599
[ ENGINE REVVING ]

147
00:24:54,280 --> 00:24:57,949
[ MAN ] He comes in, he does his job,
and then he goes home.

148
00:24:57,950 --> 00:25:00,779
Other than that,
I really don't know what to tell you.

149
00:25:00,780 --> 00:25:02,739
Interns pretty much work around the clock.

150
00:25:02,740 --> 00:25:04,079
We don't have much of a life.

151
00:25:04,080 --> 00:25:06,539
You know where we can find him?

152
00:25:06,790 --> 00:25:12,789
No. Um... You can try him at home, or you
will have to wait till he gets back.

153
00:25:15,050 --> 00:25:17,299
He's not in some kind of trouble, is he?

154
00:25:41,780 --> 00:25:43,029
[ PHONE RINGING ]

155
00:26:00,340 --> 00:26:02,549
[ ANSWERING MACHINE CLICKS ]

156
00:26:02,550 --> 00:26:05,729
This is Michael. I am not in right now.
Please leave a message.

157
00:26:05,730 --> 00:26:06,679
[ ANSWERING MACHINE BEEPS ]

158
00:26:06,680 --> 00:26:10,439
Hey, Michael, it's Adam. The police were
just in the hospital looking for you.

159
00:26:10,440 --> 00:26:13,779
They were convinced you were
involved with a shoot-out.

160
00:26:13,780 --> 00:26:16,819
I told them there's no way you'd be
involved with something like that,

161
00:26:16,820 --> 00:26:19,149
but they're looking for you. Right now.

162
00:26:23,320 --> 00:26:25,069
Why are they after you?

163
00:26:49,480 --> 00:26:50,979
Shit!

164
00:26:53,020 --> 00:26:54,899
[ALL SNARLING]

165
00:27:37,480 --> 00:27:38,859
Hello, Michael.

166
00:27:56,920 --> 00:27:58,579
[ SCREAMS ]

167
00:29:06,270 --> 00:29:07,769
What the fuck is going on?

168
00:30:53,010 --> 00:30:54,839
Stop the car.

169
00:30:56,600 --> 00:30:57,679
Stop the car!

170
00:30:58,350 --> 00:30:59,849
Back off!

171
00:30:59,850 --> 00:31:01,099
Okay.

172
00:31:02,450 --> 00:31:03,699
Okay.

173
00:31:05,360 --> 00:31:06,689
All right.

174
00:31:10,030 --> 00:31:12,189
But you have lost a lot of blood.

175
00:31:12,490 --> 00:31:15,239
If you don't stop the car,
you're going to get us both killed.

176
00:31:17,370 --> 00:31:20,199
I am not screwing around!
Neither am I.

177
00:31:20,200 --> 00:31:22,119
Now shut up and hold on.
I will be fine.

178
00:31:27,920 --> 00:31:29,499
Shit...

179
00:33:10,480 --> 00:33:13,439
A second escape. Impressive.

180
00:33:13,440 --> 00:33:15,649
Perhaps Raze wasn't overstating matters.

181
00:33:15,650 --> 00:33:18,489
Raze didn't bring back this.

182
00:33:26,540 --> 00:33:28,039
[CHUCKLING]

183
00:33:30,460 --> 00:33:36,959
If Michael is indeed The Carrier, the
Vampires could... Relax, old friend.

184
00:33:37,170 --> 00:33:38,839
I have tasted his flesh.

185
00:33:39,760 --> 00:33:41,929
Just two days till full moon.

186
00:33:43,140 --> 00:33:45,719
Soon, he will be a Lycan.

187
00:33:46,310 --> 00:33:49,439
Soon, he will come looking for us.

188
00:34:10,040 --> 00:34:13,209
It's a shame we don't have more.

189
00:34:27,520 --> 00:34:29,729
Positive.

190
00:35:15,610 --> 00:35:18,819
Lay still.
Your skull's taken a good knock.

191
00:35:19,610 --> 00:35:21,989
You have been unconscious for a while.

192
00:35:22,650 --> 00:35:26,449
Do you have any idea
why those men were after you?

193
00:35:26,780 --> 00:35:28,529
Where am I?

194
00:35:29,450 --> 00:35:31,199
You're safe.

195
00:35:35,130 --> 00:35:36,999
I am Selene.

196
00:35:49,390 --> 00:35:52,429
So for once, the rumours were true.

197
00:35:55,270 --> 00:36:00,069
The whole house has been absolutely
buzzing about your new pet.

198
00:36:01,740 --> 00:36:07,029
Oh, God. You're going to try to turn him,
aren't you? Of course not.

199
00:36:07,530 --> 00:36:10,239
So why did you bring him here?

200
00:36:12,410 --> 00:36:13,789
He saved my life.

201
00:36:17,040 --> 00:36:18,039
Why are you here?

202
00:36:18,040 --> 00:36:19,209
Kraven sent me.

203
00:36:19,210 --> 00:36:22,129
He wants to see you. Now.

204
00:36:24,930 --> 00:36:27,299
This is completely unacceptable!

205
00:36:29,010 --> 00:36:32,639
You go against my orders and spend the
night away from the shelter of the mansion

206
00:36:32,640 --> 00:36:36,229
with a human? A human you have
since brought back to my house.

207
00:36:36,230 --> 00:36:40,609
As far as I am concerned,
this is still Viktor's house.

208
00:36:42,110 --> 00:36:44,029
Look, I don't want to argue.

209
00:36:44,030 --> 00:36:47,319
I just need you to understand that Michael
is somehow important to the Lycans...

210
00:36:47,320 --> 00:36:50,569
Oh, so now it's "Michael"!
Kraven, would you just hear me out?

211
00:36:50,570 --> 00:36:54,369
It's just beyond me why you're so
obsessed over this ridiculous theory.

212
00:36:54,370 --> 00:36:59,789
Lucian wouldn't be the slightest bit
interested in a human, Michael or otherwise.

213
00:37:01,840 --> 00:37:04,129
Wait a minute.

214
00:37:05,720 --> 00:37:10,219
You're infatuated with him, aren't you?
Now, that's a ridiculous theory.

215
00:37:10,850 --> 00:37:12,179
Is it?

216
00:37:48,090 --> 00:37:49,759
[ SCREAMS ]

217
00:37:49,760 --> 00:37:50,929
[ HISSES ]

218
00:38:11,110 --> 00:38:12,359
[ SCREAMS ]

219
00:38:13,120 --> 00:38:15,949
[ DOGS BARKING ]

220
00:38:36,350 --> 00:38:38,639
Leave us!

221
00:39:12,680 --> 00:39:15,219
I sure hope you never get
pissed off with me.

222
00:39:15,220 --> 00:39:17,009
Hold on.

223
00:39:19,270 --> 00:39:20,969
Check this out.

224
00:39:25,860 --> 00:39:28,439
Go ahead. Squeeze off a few.

225
00:39:41,000 --> 00:39:43,119
Eject the mag.

226
00:39:46,380 --> 00:39:50,129
You have copied the Lycan rounds.
Silver nitrate.

227
00:39:50,130 --> 00:39:51,959
A lethal dose.

228
00:39:51,960 --> 00:39:54,629
They won't dig these out,
like they do with our usual rounds.

229
00:39:54,630 --> 00:39:58,219
Straight into the bloodstream.
Ain't nothing to dig out.

230
00:40:02,520 --> 00:40:03,520
[ SELENE ] Tell me, Kahn.

231
00:40:04,730 --> 00:40:07,399
Do you believe Lucian died
the way they say he did?

232
00:40:07,400 --> 00:40:09,229
Kraven been telling
war stories again, is he?

233
00:40:09,230 --> 00:40:10,819
That's my point.

234
00:40:10,820 --> 00:40:14,189
It's nothing but an ancient story.
His story.

235
00:40:14,190 --> 00:40:17,569
There's not a shred of proof
he killed Lucian, only his word.

236
00:40:17,570 --> 00:40:20,739
I have never underestimated
Kraven's lust for advancement,

237
00:40:20,740 --> 00:40:23,789
but Viktor believed him,
and that's all that matters.

238
00:40:23,790 --> 00:40:25,619
Now, where you going with this anyway?

239
00:40:25,620 --> 00:40:26,789
Nowhere.

240
00:40:48,560 --> 00:40:51,939
Engaging Death Dealers in public
and she has to run after some human

241
00:40:51,940 --> 00:40:53,529
was not what I had in mind.

242
00:40:53,530 --> 00:40:56,359
You were told...
You were told to set up shop and lay low!

243
00:40:56,360 --> 00:40:59,619
Calm yourself, Kraven!

244
00:41:01,490 --> 00:41:05,289
The human doesn't concern you.

245
00:41:06,160 --> 00:41:11,339
And besides, I have laid low
for quite long enough.

246
00:41:22,010 --> 00:41:24,469
Just keep your men at bay, Lucian.

247
00:41:24,470 --> 00:41:26,479
At least for the time being.

248
00:41:26,480 --> 00:41:30,899
Don't force me to regret our arrangement.

249
00:41:30,900 --> 00:41:33,649
You just concentrate on your part.

250
00:41:33,980 --> 00:41:38,149
Remember,
I have bled for you once already.

251
00:41:38,150 --> 00:41:40,989
Without me, you'd have nothing.

252
00:41:40,990 --> 00:41:44,489
You'd be nothing.

253
00:42:41,300 --> 00:42:43,679
[ METAL CLANGING, MEN YELLING ]

254
00:43:30,100 --> 00:43:33,439
[ SELENE ] Of the scores of brave souls
who entered Lucian's fortress

255
00:43:33,440 --> 00:43:37,519
a single Vampire survived: Kraven,

256
00:43:37,520 --> 00:43:41,489
who was richly rewarded
for not only setting the great blaze,

257
00:43:41,490 --> 00:43:45,609
but for returning with evidence
of the Lycan master's demise,

258
00:43:45,610 --> 00:43:49,789
the branded skin,
cut from Lucian's very arm.

259
00:44:18,060 --> 00:44:21,149
I have been looking for you everywhere.
Not now. He's been bitten.

260
00:44:22,940 --> 00:44:25,359
Your human, he's been marked by a Lycan.

261
00:44:28,030 --> 00:44:29,909
Did Kraven put you up to this?
No.

262
00:44:29,910 --> 00:44:33,619
I saw the wound with my own eyes,
I swear it.

263
00:44:35,710 --> 00:44:37,829
But what about the Covenant?

264
00:44:37,830 --> 00:44:40,209
You know it's forbidden!

265
00:44:47,840 --> 00:44:50,679
And ever since he bit me,
I have been...

266
00:44:51,850 --> 00:44:56,229
I have been having these hallucinations
and... And these delusions.

267
00:44:58,310 --> 00:45:02,689
All I know is, it feels like
my skull is splitting in half.

268
00:45:02,690 --> 00:45:05,439
Okay, so a full-grown man bit you?

269
00:45:08,410 --> 00:45:09,429
Jesus.

270
00:45:10,280 --> 00:45:12,029
Are you sure this wasn't a dog?

271
00:45:12,030 --> 00:45:16,109
I said, it was a man. Okay.
It was a man. Okay. I got it.

272
00:45:16,110 --> 00:45:18,119
He was after me.

273
00:45:18,120 --> 00:45:22,279
And that woman from the subway...
What woman?

274
00:45:22,750 --> 00:45:29,299
Haven't you been listening to me? She took
me hostage! All right. I am just... Please.

275
00:45:30,550 --> 00:45:34,349
I am going to help you get this all sorted
out, all right? I will be right back.

276
00:45:36,430 --> 00:45:38,389
Let go, Michael.

277
00:45:38,900 --> 00:45:40,479
Let go.

278
00:45:41,060 --> 00:45:45,229
Just calm down, okay?
I am going to be back in a minute.

279
00:45:45,230 --> 00:45:48,359
That's a promise. All right?
All right.

280
00:46:22,560 --> 00:46:23,639
[ ADAM ] Hey!

281
00:46:26,100 --> 00:46:27,239
Hey!

282
00:46:56,930 --> 00:47:02,229
Please forgive me
but I desperately need your guidance.

283
00:47:08,070 --> 00:47:10,239
Kahn wants to see you.

284
00:48:50,000 --> 00:48:51,249
[ SELENE ] To my knowledge,

285
00:48:51,250 --> 00:48:55,879
an Awakening has never been
attempted by one such as myself.

286
00:48:56,470 --> 00:49:00,049
The elders alone hold the power to organize
their memories and thoughts

287
00:49:00,050 --> 00:49:05,429
into a single, cohesive vision,
a detailed record of their reign.

288
00:49:05,430 --> 00:49:09,519
I can only hope Viktor will hear my plea.

289
00:50:18,590 --> 00:50:22,179
Please forgive me,
but I desperately need your guidance.

290
00:50:23,510 --> 00:50:26,639
I apologize for breaking the chain and
awakening you ahead of schedule,

291
00:50:26,640 --> 00:50:29,349
but I fear we may all be in grave danger.

292
00:50:30,350 --> 00:50:34,059
Especially you, my lord,
if left in your weakened state.

293
00:50:34,980 --> 00:50:37,689
For I believe that Lucian
is alive and well.

294
00:50:38,780 --> 00:50:45,409
Here. Now. In this very city, preparing to
hit us during the Awakening ceremony.

295
00:50:46,740 --> 00:50:48,869
Even more disturbing...

296
00:50:50,000 --> 00:50:51,869
is that if I am correct...

297
00:50:53,170 --> 00:50:55,839
it would mean that Kraven
is in league with him.

298
00:52:18,420 --> 00:52:20,459
What's so pressing?

299
00:52:20,960 --> 00:52:22,839
Take a look.

300
00:52:41,940 --> 00:52:43,449
Selene!

301
00:52:43,450 --> 00:52:45,819
[ OVER SPEAKERS ]
I want to speak with Selene!

302
00:52:49,660 --> 00:52:51,369
Is that Michael?

303
00:52:51,370 --> 00:52:52,789
Is it Michael?

304
00:52:52,790 --> 00:52:54,449
What the hell is going on?

305
00:52:54,450 --> 00:52:55,909
What's happening to me?

306
00:52:58,000 --> 00:52:59,039
I am coming out.

307
00:53:01,000 --> 00:53:04,629
If you go to him, you will never
be welcome in this house again.

308
00:53:07,640 --> 00:53:11,009
Now that Viktor's awake, we will see
what he has to say about that.

309
00:53:24,530 --> 00:53:25,530
Get in.

310
00:53:51,510 --> 00:53:54,559
Look, I warned her.
I warned her, but she didn't listen.

311
00:53:54,560 --> 00:53:56,389
She never listens.
I should have told you sooner.

312
00:53:56,390 --> 00:53:58,019
Told me what?

313
00:54:00,520 --> 00:54:02,899
Her human, Michael...

314
00:54:04,070 --> 00:54:06,569
he's not a human at all.

315
00:54:06,570 --> 00:54:07,899
He's a Lycan.

316
00:54:11,410 --> 00:54:12,819
What?

317
00:54:12,820 --> 00:54:16,659
[ MAN ] What's this ruckus?

318
00:54:20,670 --> 00:54:23,249
You can never come here again.
They will kill you. Do you understand?

319
00:54:23,250 --> 00:54:26,419
Why? Who are you people?

320
00:55:10,720 --> 00:55:12,089
Leave us.

321
00:55:20,430 --> 00:55:22,559
Whether you like it or not,
you're in the middle of a war

322
00:55:22,560 --> 00:55:25,059
that's been raging
for the better part of 1000 years.

323
00:55:25,060 --> 00:55:28,319
A blood feud between Vampires and Lycans.

324
00:55:30,030 --> 00:55:31,149
Werewolves.

325
00:55:44,290 --> 00:55:45,539
Consider yourself lucky.

326
00:55:45,540 --> 00:55:48,959
Most humans die within an hour
of being bitten by an immortal.

327
00:55:48,960 --> 00:55:51,009
The viruses we transmit are deadly.

328
00:55:51,010 --> 00:55:55,929
And if you bit me, what, I'd become
a Vampire instead? No, you'd die.

329
00:55:56,760 --> 00:56:00,139
No one's ever survived
a bite from both species.

330
00:56:00,140 --> 00:56:03,939
By rights, I'd stop the car and kill you
myself right... Then why are you helping me?

331
00:56:03,940 --> 00:56:07,519
I am not!
I track down and kill your kind.

332
00:56:07,520 --> 00:56:11,359
My only interest is finding out
why Lucian wants you so badly.

333
00:56:14,700 --> 00:56:17,699
Do you know why I have
been awakened, servant?

334
00:56:17,700 --> 00:56:19,699
No, my lord.

335
00:56:19,700 --> 00:56:21,039
But I will soon find out.

336
00:56:21,040 --> 00:56:23,329
You mean when you find her.

337
00:56:23,620 --> 00:56:24,999
Yes, my lord.

338
00:56:25,000 --> 00:56:27,209
You must let her come to me.

339
00:56:28,380 --> 00:56:32,879
We have much to discuss, Selene and l.

340
00:56:33,630 --> 00:56:39,099
She has shown me
a great many disturbing things.

341
00:56:39,100 --> 00:56:42,559
Things that will be dealt with soon enough.

342
00:56:42,560 --> 00:56:46,689
This coven has grown weak, decadent.

343
00:56:46,690 --> 00:56:51,319
Perhaps I should have left someone
else in charge of my affairs.

344
00:56:51,320 --> 00:56:53,609
[ HUFFING ]

345
00:56:56,780 --> 00:56:58,699
Still...

346
00:56:59,490 --> 00:57:01,829
her memories...

347
00:57:02,200 --> 00:57:04,749
are chaotic.

348
00:57:06,170 --> 00:57:07,919
There's no sense of time.

349
00:57:07,920 --> 00:57:10,419
Please, my lord, let me summon assistance.

350
00:57:10,420 --> 00:57:12,249
You're in need of rest.

351
00:57:12,750 --> 00:57:15,919
I have rested enough.

352
00:57:16,880 --> 00:57:19,889
What you will do is summon Marcus.

353
00:57:23,310 --> 00:57:26,769
But he still slumbers, my lord.

354
00:57:28,150 --> 00:57:34,109
Amelia and the Council members are
arriving tomorrow night to awaken Marcus.

355
00:57:34,780 --> 00:57:36,779
Not you, my lord.

356
00:57:36,780 --> 00:57:41,119
You have been awakened
a full century ahead of schedule.

357
00:57:49,630 --> 00:57:51,829
That bitch has betrayed me.

358
00:57:52,630 --> 00:57:56,379
Now he knows everything
she's been obsessing about.

359
00:58:00,470 --> 00:58:02,219
Wait.

360
00:58:07,140 --> 00:58:08,979
Are you to be trusted?

361
00:58:09,980 --> 00:58:11,899
Of course.

362
00:58:12,400 --> 00:58:14,399
Meet me in my quarters in 20 minutes.

363
00:58:14,400 --> 00:58:17,569
It's time I filled you in
on a few things.

364
00:58:57,610 --> 00:59:01,569
[ MICHAEL ] I am seeing these things,
these hallucinations.

365
00:59:01,570 --> 00:59:04,409
[ SELENE ] They're not hallucinations,
they're memories.

366
00:59:04,410 --> 00:59:08,369
You have been bitten. His memories
have been passed to you.

367
00:59:11,370 --> 00:59:16,709
This is one of the places we use
for interrogations. It should be safe.

368
00:59:31,890 --> 00:59:33,439
[ MICHAEL ] Ziodex lndustries.

369
00:59:33,440 --> 00:59:34,769
We own it.

370
00:59:34,770 --> 00:59:37,729
First there was synthetic plasma, now this.

371
00:59:37,730 --> 00:59:40,739
Once it's approved,
it should be our newest cash crop.

372
00:59:40,740 --> 00:59:42,779
It's cloned blood.

373
00:59:48,660 --> 00:59:49,829
What are these for?

374
00:59:51,910 --> 00:59:53,959
Lycans are allergic to silver.

375
00:59:53,960 --> 00:59:57,749
If we don't get our bullets out quickly enough,
they end up dying on us during questioning.

376
00:59:58,590 --> 01:00:00,249
What do you do with them afterwards?

377
01:00:01,760 --> 01:00:03,669
We put the bullets back in.

378
01:00:19,360 --> 01:00:20,779
How are things progressing?

379
01:00:20,780 --> 01:00:22,279
We're ready.

380
01:00:28,450 --> 01:00:30,949
Why do you hate them so much?

381
01:00:31,540 --> 01:00:34,249
I have already told you,
we're at war.

382
01:00:34,250 --> 01:00:36,119
So you're just following orders?

383
01:00:44,800 --> 01:00:47,969
Why can't you just answer the question?

384
01:00:50,510 --> 01:00:52,059
Fine.

385
01:00:53,390 --> 01:00:55,809
Something was in the stable...

386
01:00:56,020 --> 01:00:58,979
tearing our horses to pieces.

387
01:01:00,360 --> 01:01:02,899
I couldn't have saved my mother.

388
01:01:02,900 --> 01:01:05,489
Or my sister.

389
01:01:05,860 --> 01:01:08,529
Their screams woke me.

390
01:01:09,120 --> 01:01:13,329
My father died outside,
trying to fend them off.

391
01:01:13,950 --> 01:01:16,499
I stood at my door...

392
01:01:17,080 --> 01:01:20,329
about to run to my nieces' room when.

393
01:01:20,330 --> 01:01:22,839
[ GIRLS WHIMPERING ]

394
01:01:26,590 --> 01:01:28,879
Twin girls.

395
01:01:31,510 --> 01:01:34,059
Barely 6 years old.

396
01:01:35,350 --> 01:01:37,999
Butchered like animals.

397
01:01:38,850 --> 01:01:40,189
Jesus Christ.

398
01:01:40,190 --> 01:01:43,359
The next thing I knew,
I was in his arms.

399
01:01:43,820 --> 01:01:46,819
The war had spilled into our house.

400
01:01:46,820 --> 01:01:49,909
He'd been tracking the Lycans for days.

401
01:01:49,910 --> 01:01:52,319
He drove them off and saved me.

402
01:01:52,320 --> 01:01:53,699
Who?

403
01:01:53,700 --> 01:01:55,159
Viktor.

404
01:01:56,370 --> 01:01:59,329
The oldest and strongest of us.

405
01:01:59,790 --> 01:02:02,879
That night, he made me a Vampire.

406
01:02:03,380 --> 01:02:06,379
He gave me the strength
to avenge my family.

407
01:02:06,380 --> 01:02:09,379
Since then, I have never looked back.

408
01:02:15,720 --> 01:02:18,139
I saw your pictures.

409
01:02:18,890 --> 01:02:21,059
Who is the woman, your wife?

410
01:02:29,650 --> 01:02:34,409
It may be wise to keep a closer eye
on our cousins.

411
01:02:34,910 --> 01:02:38,329
I will have Raze see to it immediately.

412
01:02:38,330 --> 01:02:42,919
I am afraid that I am going to have
to place my faith in you, my friend.

413
01:02:43,340 --> 01:02:46,749
Time is running short.

414
01:02:46,750 --> 01:02:50,339
[ MICHAEL ] I tried to swerve,
but he hit us anyway.

415
01:02:52,590 --> 01:02:55,259
He sent us right into the oncoming lane.

416
01:02:59,100 --> 01:03:01,269
When I came to, I...

417
01:03:02,270 --> 01:03:06,189
I realized that part of the engine
was in the front seat.

418
01:03:07,030 --> 01:03:12,859
And she was pinned there,
6 inches from me...

419
01:03:14,700 --> 01:03:17,449
in this horrible position.

420
01:03:21,540 --> 01:03:23,829
I think she was in shock because she just

421
01:03:23,830 --> 01:03:27,379
kept asking me over
and over again if I was all right.

422
01:03:29,970 --> 01:03:31,759
She was more worried about me.

423
01:03:35,890 --> 01:03:39,889
You know, if I knew then what
I know now, I could have saved her.

424
01:03:41,560 --> 01:03:44,269
There's no doubt in my mind about that.

425
01:03:45,730 --> 01:03:48,149
But instead she died right there...

426
01:03:49,400 --> 01:03:52,569
about two minutes before
the ambulance arrived.

427
01:03:57,410 --> 01:04:01,079
After that, I didn't see
any reason to stick around.

428
01:04:01,080 --> 01:04:06,249
I spent a summer here with
my grandfather when I was a kid so...

429
01:04:06,250 --> 01:04:09,249
After I got my degree, I just...

430
01:04:10,010 --> 01:04:11,759
I took off.

431
01:04:14,430 --> 01:04:19,429
I came over here to move on, to forget.

432
01:04:22,180 --> 01:04:25,019
It seemed like a good idea at the time.

433
01:04:27,360 --> 01:04:29,359
And have you?

434
01:04:30,940 --> 01:04:32,189
Moved on?

435
01:04:33,950 --> 01:04:35,699
Have you?

436
01:04:44,960 --> 01:04:49,209
I need you to keep what I am about to
tell you under the strictest confidence.

437
01:04:49,210 --> 01:04:51,379
It can wait.

438
01:05:17,410 --> 01:05:18,909
[ MICHAEL ] Who started the war?

439
01:05:19,280 --> 01:05:20,739
[ SELENE ] They did.

440
01:05:20,740 --> 01:05:24,539
Or at least that's what
we have been led to believe.

441
01:05:24,870 --> 01:05:27,919
Digging into the past is forbidden.

442
01:05:29,750 --> 01:05:31,749
I should be heading back.

443
01:05:31,750 --> 01:05:33,919
What about me?

444
01:05:33,920 --> 01:05:36,469
Viktor will know what to do.
I will come back tomorrow night.

445
01:05:36,470 --> 01:05:37,799
I am not staying here alone.

446
01:05:37,800 --> 01:05:40,679
You will if you want to live.
No, I want to go with you.

447
01:05:59,160 --> 01:06:01,119
What are you doing?

448
01:06:04,410 --> 01:06:06,329
When the full moon rises tomorrow night,

449
01:06:06,330 --> 01:06:10,369
you will change, you will kill,
and you will feed.

450
01:06:10,370 --> 01:06:12,459
It's unavoidable.

451
01:06:12,460 --> 01:06:15,669
I can't leave you free to roam around.
I am sorry.

452
01:06:21,970 --> 01:06:25,259
A single round won't kill you, but the
silver should prevent the transformation.

453
01:06:25,260 --> 01:06:27,469
At least for a few hours.

454
01:06:27,470 --> 01:06:30,769
If I don't return in time,
do yourself a favour.

455
01:06:31,230 --> 01:06:33,229
Use it.

456
01:07:49,560 --> 01:07:52,559
[PHONE BUZZING]

457
01:07:54,810 --> 01:07:56,059
Yeah?

458
01:07:56,060 --> 01:07:59,939
[ MAN ] My lord. She's here.

459
01:08:14,290 --> 01:08:18,129
How could you do this to me?
Embarrass me like this?

460
01:08:18,130 --> 01:08:21,089
The entire coven knows
that I had plans for us.

461
01:08:21,090 --> 01:08:23,129
There is no us!

462
01:08:23,130 --> 01:08:25,179
You will go before Viktor...

463
01:08:25,180 --> 01:08:30,969
and tell him exactly what I tell you to!
From here on out, you will do as I say.

464
01:08:30,970 --> 01:08:33,559
Is that in any way unclear?

465
01:09:19,860 --> 01:09:22,689
Come closer, my child.

466
01:09:24,740 --> 01:09:26,359
Outside.

467
01:09:26,910 --> 01:09:28,909
Come on, move it.

468
01:09:38,420 --> 01:09:40,999
I have been lost without you, my lord.

469
01:09:41,000 --> 01:09:45,009
Constantly hounded by Kraven
and his never-ending infatuation.

470
01:09:45,010 --> 01:09:46,339
[CHUCKLING]

471
01:09:47,630 --> 01:09:51,299
It is the oldest story in the book.

472
01:09:51,300 --> 01:09:56,479
He desires the one thing he cannot have.

473
01:09:58,390 --> 01:10:01,609
Now, tell me...

474
01:10:02,360 --> 01:10:05,859
why have you come to believe
that Lucian still lives?

475
01:10:05,860 --> 01:10:07,399
[ PHONE BEEPS ]

476
01:10:07,400 --> 01:10:08,569
Yeah.

477
01:10:08,570 --> 01:10:10,699
But I have given you all
the proof you need.

478
01:10:10,700 --> 01:10:15,949
Incoherent thoughts and
images, nothing more.

479
01:10:15,950 --> 01:10:19,539
Which is precisely why the Awakening
is performed by an elder.

480
01:10:19,540 --> 01:10:22,039
You do not possess the necessary skills.

481
01:10:22,040 --> 01:10:25,049
But I did see Lucian. I shot him.
You must believe me.

482
01:10:25,050 --> 01:10:28,379
The chain has never been broken.
Not once.

483
01:10:28,380 --> 01:10:30,799
Not in 14 centuries.

484
01:10:30,800 --> 01:10:35,059
Not since we elders first began
to leapfrog through time.

485
01:10:35,060 --> 01:10:38,309
One awake, two asleep.
That's the way of it.

486
01:10:38,310 --> 01:10:41,889
It is Marcus' turn to reign, not mine.

487
01:10:41,890 --> 01:10:43,229
There's been a little complication.

488
01:10:43,230 --> 01:10:44,819
But I had no choice.

489
01:10:44,820 --> 01:10:47,649
The coven is in danger,
and Michael is the key... [ SCOFFS ]

490
01:10:50,740 --> 01:10:51,779
Ah, yes.

491
01:10:53,070 --> 01:10:55,239
The Lycan.

492
01:10:57,290 --> 01:10:59,249
Please.

493
01:10:59,750 --> 01:11:02,079
Give me the chance
to get the proof you require.

494
01:11:02,080 --> 01:11:03,419
Fine.

495
01:11:03,420 --> 01:11:07,589
VIKTOR: I will leave it to Kraven
to collect the proof...

496
01:11:08,090 --> 01:11:10,759
if there is any.

497
01:11:12,090 --> 01:11:14,089
How could you trust him over me?

498
01:11:14,090 --> 01:11:19,429
Because he is not the one who
has been tainted by an animal.

499
01:11:21,640 --> 01:11:24,019
I love you...

500
01:11:26,480 --> 01:11:30,739
like a daughter,
but you leave me with no choice.

501
01:11:30,740 --> 01:11:33,949
These rules are in place
for a good reason,

502
01:11:33,950 --> 01:11:39,449
and they are the only reason
we have survived this long.

503
01:11:43,580 --> 01:11:47,539
You will not be shown
an ounce of leniency.

504
01:11:48,050 --> 01:11:53,549
When Amelia arrives, the Council
will convene and decide your fate.

505
01:11:54,140 --> 01:11:57,299
You have broken the chain
and the Covenant!

506
01:11:57,300 --> 01:11:59,889
You must be judged!

507
01:12:24,170 --> 01:12:27,329
You should have listened to me
and stayed out of this.

508
01:12:27,330 --> 01:12:32,049
Now you will be lucky if I can convince
the Council to spare your life.

509
01:12:32,050 --> 01:12:33,969
Tell me.

510
01:12:33,970 --> 01:12:38,599
Did you have the nerve to cut the skin
from his arm, or did Lucian do it for you?

511
01:12:44,600 --> 01:12:46,849
Mark my words.

512
01:12:46,850 --> 01:12:49,939
Soon, you will be seeing things my way.

513
01:12:56,030 --> 01:12:57,779
[LOCK RATTLING]

514
01:12:59,950 --> 01:13:03,539
No one opens this door.
Understood?

515
01:13:05,210 --> 01:13:09,289
I can't afford to have my future queen
run off with that Lycan again.

516
01:13:47,750 --> 01:13:49,419
Shit.

517
01:13:59,590 --> 01:14:03,679
Change of plans. Amelia will be
picked up by Soren and his team.

518
01:14:03,680 --> 01:14:05,099
That's our job.

519
01:14:05,100 --> 01:14:07,769
Not any more.

520
01:15:11,620 --> 01:15:13,749
[ LYCANS SNARLING ]
[ WOMEN SCREAMING ]

521
01:15:15,840 --> 01:15:18,209
[ GUNFIRE ]

522
01:15:34,690 --> 01:15:38,189
[ DOGS BARKING ]

523
01:16:39,250 --> 01:16:41,049
[ ALARM RINGING ]

524
01:16:59,320 --> 01:17:00,479
Why are you helping me?

525
01:17:00,480 --> 01:17:03,399
I am not. I am helping me.

526
01:17:42,190 --> 01:17:43,189
What's going on?

527
01:17:43,190 --> 01:17:45,989
The perimeter sensor's been tripped.

528
01:17:45,990 --> 01:17:48,569
We're locking down the mansion.

529
01:17:49,030 --> 01:17:52,289
It's Selene. She's escaped,
to go to him, to Michael.

530
01:17:52,790 --> 01:17:57,619
I want that Lycan's head on a plate.

531
01:18:45,460 --> 01:18:46,460
[ SCREAMS ]

532
01:19:28,420 --> 01:19:30,219
We need to go.

533
01:19:59,500 --> 01:20:00,619
Get down!

534
01:20:03,460 --> 01:20:06,169
- Go.
- Go.

535
01:20:12,220 --> 01:20:14,509
Jump.
Are you fucking kidding me?

536
01:21:04,350 --> 01:21:05,389
[TIRES SCREECHING]

537
01:21:18,030 --> 01:21:21,029
[MAN GASPING]

538
01:21:37,050 --> 01:21:38,049
Any luck?

539
01:21:38,050 --> 01:21:40,049
False alarm.

540
01:21:40,050 --> 01:21:44,679
The dogs would have been all over it if
anything had gotten even near that fence.

541
01:21:44,680 --> 01:21:47,229
Amelia should have arrived by now.
Yes.

542
01:21:52,730 --> 01:21:57,029
Look, I want you to slip off the property
and find out what's keeping her.

543
01:21:57,030 --> 01:21:58,989
You have got it.

544
01:22:04,410 --> 01:22:06,449
[ LYCAN SNARLS ]

545
01:22:12,460 --> 01:22:14,049
[ SNARLS ]

546
01:22:32,110 --> 01:22:33,609
[ PANTING ]

547
01:22:37,190 --> 01:22:39,819
Maybe we should pull over and dose him.

548
01:22:39,820 --> 01:22:42,989
Fuck him. He will be all right.
We're almost there.

549
01:23:11,810 --> 01:23:13,309
[ GRUNTS ]

550
01:23:24,490 --> 01:23:27,199
[RADIO PLAYING WILD ROCK MUSIC]

551
01:23:46,640 --> 01:23:48,179
[ YELLS ]

552
01:23:48,180 --> 01:23:52,189
Oh, shit. He's not going to make it.
Pull over. Pull over!

553
01:24:11,080 --> 01:24:12,709
Get the kit.

554
01:24:26,260 --> 01:24:28,389
- Stick him.
- Stick him.

555
01:24:39,610 --> 01:24:41,359
My lord.

556
01:24:42,490 --> 01:24:45,149
Viktor wants to speak with you.

557
01:25:10,680 --> 01:25:12,519
My lord.

558
01:25:16,900 --> 01:25:19,559
I sent for Selene...

559
01:25:19,940 --> 01:25:21,979
not you.

560
01:25:22,570 --> 01:25:25,239
She's defied your orders and...

561
01:25:27,030 --> 01:25:28,949
fled the mansion, my lord.

562
01:25:28,950 --> 01:25:34,249
Your incompetence
is becoming most taxing.

563
01:25:34,250 --> 01:25:37,369
It's not my fault.
She's become obsessed,

564
01:25:37,370 --> 01:25:40,959
thinks that I am at the core
of some ridiculous conspiracy.

565
01:25:40,960 --> 01:25:43,129
[ SELENE ] And here's my proof.

566
01:25:43,130 --> 01:25:45,209
[ YELLS ]

567
01:25:57,390 --> 01:26:00,649
Now, I want you to tell them
exactly what you told me.

568
01:26:03,150 --> 01:26:04,149
[ CRUNCH ]

569
01:26:04,150 --> 01:26:06,319
[ YELLS ]

570
01:26:08,320 --> 01:26:11,489
All right, all right.

571
01:26:12,990 --> 01:26:18,159
We have been searching for someone
with a special trait.

572
01:26:18,160 --> 01:26:22,419
A direct descendant of
Alexander Corvinus...

573
01:26:22,420 --> 01:26:24,339
Hungarian...

574
01:26:24,340 --> 01:26:26,379
a warlord...

575
01:26:26,380 --> 01:26:31,139
who came to power in the early
seasons of the fifth century.

576
01:26:31,140 --> 01:26:37,769
Just in time to watch a plague
ravage his village.

577
01:26:38,850 --> 01:26:42,019
He alone survived.

578
01:26:43,320 --> 01:26:48,149
Somehow, his body
was able to change the disease,

579
01:26:48,150 --> 01:26:52,159
mould it to his benefit.

580
01:26:52,160 --> 01:26:57,499
He became the first true immortal.

581
01:27:02,710 --> 01:27:04,459
[ CRUNCH ] [ YELLS ]

582
01:27:06,000 --> 01:27:12,299
And years later, he fathered at least two
children who inherited this same trait.

583
01:27:12,300 --> 01:27:15,759
The sons of the Corvinus clan.

584
01:27:15,760 --> 01:27:19,139
One bitten by bat, one by wolf,

585
01:27:19,140 --> 01:27:24,809
one to walk the lonely road
of mortality as a human.

586
01:27:24,810 --> 01:27:28,069
It's a ridiculous legend. Nothing!

587
01:27:29,820 --> 01:27:31,319
That may be...

588
01:27:32,160 --> 01:27:35,449
but our species do have a common ancestor.

589
01:27:36,330 --> 01:27:42,369
A mutation of the original virus
is directly linked to his bloodline.

590
01:27:42,370 --> 01:27:47,379
There is a descendant
of Corvinus lying there...

591
01:27:48,590 --> 01:27:50,669
not three feet from you.

592
01:27:50,670 --> 01:27:51,670
Yes.

593
01:27:53,300 --> 01:27:58,389
But he's already a Vampire.
We needed a pure source.

594
01:27:59,270 --> 01:28:04,519
Untainted. An exact duplicate
of the original virus...

595
01:28:04,900 --> 01:28:11,439
which we learned... was hidden away in the
genetic code of his human descendants

596
01:28:11,440 --> 01:28:16,619
and passed along in its latent form...

597
01:28:17,870 --> 01:28:20,699
down through the ages...

598
01:28:20,700 --> 01:28:25,709
all the way to Michael Corvin.

599
01:28:26,880 --> 01:28:31,799
For years, we tried to combine
their bloodlines.

600
01:28:35,220 --> 01:28:38,389
And for years we failed.

601
01:28:38,930 --> 01:28:41,099
It was useless.

602
01:28:42,480 --> 01:28:47,149
Even at the cellular level, our species
seemed destined to destroy each other.

603
01:28:49,730 --> 01:28:54,649
That is, until we found Michael.

604
01:28:57,820 --> 01:29:02,909
The Corvinus strain allows
for a perfect union.

605
01:29:05,080 --> 01:29:08,419
A triple-celled platelet...

606
01:29:09,590 --> 01:29:14,509
which holds unspeakable power.

607
01:29:14,930 --> 01:29:18,139
There can be no such union.

608
01:29:18,970 --> 01:29:21,449
And to speak of it is heresy.

609
01:29:21,450 --> 01:29:23,559
We will see.

610
01:29:24,770 --> 01:29:29,189
Once Lucian has injected himself
with Michael's blood.

611
01:29:29,690 --> 01:29:31,359
Lucian is dead.

612
01:29:31,360 --> 01:29:35,029
According to whom?

613
01:29:45,460 --> 01:29:47,499
I need you to do something for me.

614
01:29:54,460 --> 01:29:59,889
I can assure you, my child
Kraven will pay with his life.

615
01:30:20,950 --> 01:30:25,239
Soon, this house will lie in ruins.

616
01:30:25,240 --> 01:30:27,869
Not before you.
No, no, no, wait. Wait!

617
01:30:27,870 --> 01:30:31,039
You and you alone
will know the truth of this.

618
01:30:34,880 --> 01:30:40,469
If Lucian was able to get his hands
on the blood of a Pure-Born,

619
01:30:40,470 --> 01:30:45,719
a powerful elder like Amelia...

620
01:30:45,720 --> 01:30:49,599
or yourself...

621
01:30:49,600 --> 01:30:54,439
and inject it along
with Michael's blood.

622
01:30:54,440 --> 01:30:56,779
Abomination.

623
01:30:56,780 --> 01:30:59,109
Half-Vampire,

624
01:30:59,110 --> 01:31:03,619
half-Lycan, but stronger than both.

625
01:31:22,720 --> 01:31:24,089
I need to speak with Kahn.

626
01:31:31,690 --> 01:31:33,399
My lord.

627
01:31:34,690 --> 01:31:38,029
The Council members
have been assassinated.

628
01:31:41,400 --> 01:31:43,159
What of Amelia?

629
01:31:43,160 --> 01:31:44,699
They bled her dry.

630
01:31:47,490 --> 01:31:50,959
It has already begun, huh?

631
01:31:51,920 --> 01:31:54,169
[ CHUCKLING ]

632
01:32:02,510 --> 01:32:04,929
I am sorry I doubted you.

633
01:32:05,510 --> 01:32:10,769
Fear not, my child,
absolution will be yours...

634
01:32:12,640 --> 01:32:17,729
the moment you kill the descendant
of Corvinus, this...

635
01:32:18,360 --> 01:32:20,569
Michael.

636
01:32:56,100 --> 01:33:00,439
You have been given an enzyme
to stop the change.

637
01:33:00,440 --> 01:33:06,069
It may take a little time
for the grogginess to dissipate.

638
01:33:12,620 --> 01:33:14,409
That's enough!

639
01:33:14,410 --> 01:33:19,039
Just... go and see
what's keeping Raze, will you?

640
01:33:20,710 --> 01:33:22,419
I really must apologize.

641
01:33:23,090 --> 01:33:26,009
He's in desperate need
of a lesson in manners.

642
01:33:26,470 --> 01:33:29,969
Speaking of manners, where are mine?
Forgive me.

643
01:33:29,970 --> 01:33:32,219
I am Lucian.

644
01:33:34,310 --> 01:33:36,599
I need to go.

645
01:33:37,980 --> 01:33:39,519
I need to get back.

646
01:33:41,150 --> 01:33:43,609
There's no going back.

647
01:33:44,280 --> 01:33:46,779
There's no going anywhere.

648
01:33:46,780 --> 01:33:51,909
The Vampires will kill you on sight.
Just for being what you are.

649
01:33:51,910 --> 01:33:53,869
One of us.

650
01:33:57,120 --> 01:34:00,129
You are one of us.

651
01:34:03,380 --> 01:34:06,129
What are you doing?

652
01:34:06,130 --> 01:34:08,879
Bringing an end to this conflict.

653
01:34:15,850 --> 01:34:18,479
Your war, it has nothing to do with me.

654
01:34:18,480 --> 01:34:20,599
My war?

655
01:34:43,420 --> 01:34:44,420
No!

656
01:35:27,210 --> 01:35:29,009
- No!
- No!

657
01:35:38,560 --> 01:35:40,279
Sonja...

658
01:36:45,880 --> 01:36:48,959
They forced you to watch her die.

659
01:36:51,300 --> 01:36:53,169
Sonja.

660
01:36:54,800 --> 01:36:57,469
That's what started the war.

661
01:37:00,770 --> 01:37:03,979
I saw it happen as if I were there.

662
01:37:09,150 --> 01:37:11,729
We were slaves once.

663
01:37:12,900 --> 01:37:16,659
The daylight guardians of the Vampires.

664
01:37:18,490 --> 01:37:21,199
I was born in servitude...

665
01:37:23,000 --> 01:37:25,829
yet I harboured them no ill will.

666
01:37:26,790 --> 01:37:29,709
I even took a Vampire for my bride.

667
01:37:30,670 --> 01:37:32,669
It was forbidden...

668
01:37:32,920 --> 01:37:35,169
our union.

669
01:37:35,170 --> 01:37:40,299
Viktor feared a blending of the species.

670
01:37:42,100 --> 01:37:44,389
Feared it so much...

671
01:37:45,520 --> 01:37:47,559
he killed her.

672
01:37:48,650 --> 01:37:50,859
His own daughter...

673
01:37:52,030 --> 01:37:54,279
burnt alive...

674
01:37:56,700 --> 01:37:58,659
for loving me.

675
01:38:01,780 --> 01:38:04,489
This is his war...

676
01:38:04,490 --> 01:38:06,709
Viktor's...

677
01:38:08,080 --> 01:38:15,169
and he's spent the last 600 years
exterminating my species.

678
01:38:16,380 --> 01:38:19,049
What are they going to do to Selene?

679
01:38:21,890 --> 01:38:23,389
We have company.

680
01:38:24,810 --> 01:38:26,519
I thought we had a deal.

681
01:38:26,520 --> 01:38:28,639
LUCIAN: Patience.

682
01:38:30,770 --> 01:38:32,399
Kraven.

683
01:38:32,400 --> 01:38:35,899
These are matters
to be discussed in private.

684
01:38:36,900 --> 01:38:41,569
Please escort our guests downstairs.

685
01:38:57,510 --> 01:39:00,589
The Council has been destroyed.

686
01:39:01,430 --> 01:39:04,259
Soon, you will have it all.

687
01:39:04,260 --> 01:39:10,439
Both great covens and an ironclad
peace treaty with the Lycans.

688
01:39:10,440 --> 01:39:14,979
Who I trust will not be forgotten
when the spoils are tabulated.

689
01:39:14,980 --> 01:39:19,239
How do you expect me to assume control
now that Viktor's been awakened?

690
01:39:19,240 --> 01:39:22,949
There's no defeating him.
He grows stronger as we speak.

691
01:39:22,950 --> 01:39:27,289
And that is precisely why I need Michael.

692
01:39:27,290 --> 01:39:29,789
If Viktor were so easy to dispatch...

693
01:39:30,370 --> 01:39:33,459
you'd have done
it yourself centuries ago.

694
01:39:36,800 --> 01:39:38,959
[METAL CREAKING]

695
01:39:44,300 --> 01:39:46,559
Exit shaft! Move it!

696
01:39:49,600 --> 01:39:51,439
Son of a bitch!

697
01:40:05,780 --> 01:40:07,949
Oh, shit!

698
01:40:20,970 --> 01:40:22,629
It's Viktor.

699
01:40:22,630 --> 01:40:24,429
Yes.

700
01:40:24,890 --> 01:40:28,179
And if you had done your job,
he'd still be in hibernation.

701
01:40:34,190 --> 01:40:36,059
Where the hell is Raze?

702
01:40:39,230 --> 01:40:41,359
Is there another way out?

703
01:40:42,200 --> 01:40:47,659
I guess it never occurred to you that you might
actually have to bleed to pull off this little coup.

704
01:40:51,250 --> 01:40:53,869
Don't even think about leaving.

705
01:41:06,180 --> 01:41:07,799
[GASPING]

706
01:41:15,390 --> 01:41:19,309
Silver nitrate.
Bet you weren't expecting that.

707
01:41:28,570 --> 01:41:31,579
Come on! Move! Move! Move!
Move! Move!

708
01:42:54,160 --> 01:42:55,789
Lucian.

709
01:43:50,630 --> 01:43:52,339
[GROWLS]

710
01:44:51,780 --> 01:44:52,780
Selene!

711
01:44:54,780 --> 01:44:55,780
Selene!

712
01:45:42,750 --> 01:45:44,579
Not yet.

713
01:50:00,590 --> 01:50:02,749
[LYCAN SNARLING]

714
01:50:18,650 --> 01:50:20,189
[GUNFIRE]

715
01:50:34,620 --> 01:50:37,039
I have to get you out.
Viktor's on his way.

716
01:50:37,040 --> 01:50:40,169
And he won't be satisfied
until every Lycan's dead.

717
01:50:41,040 --> 01:50:43,629
They will kill you too,
just for helping me.

718
01:50:43,960 --> 01:50:45,339
I know.

719
01:51:08,570 --> 01:51:10,909
I know what started the war.

720
01:53:05,600 --> 01:53:08,479
[GASPING]

721
01:53:21,040 --> 01:53:22,949
That's enough.
You're coming with me!

722
01:53:24,000 --> 01:53:26,579
I hope I live long enough to see
Viktor choke the life from you!

723
01:53:26,790 --> 01:53:28,789
I bet you do.

724
01:53:29,290 --> 01:53:32,959
But let me tell you a little something
about your beloved dark father.

725
01:53:34,130 --> 01:53:36,629
He's the one who killed your family.

726
01:53:36,970 --> 01:53:38,799
Not the Lycans.

727
01:53:39,300 --> 01:53:41,509
Never could follow his own rules.

728
01:53:41,510 --> 01:53:44,099
Said he couldn't abide
the taste of livestock.

729
01:53:44,100 --> 01:53:48,479
So every once in a while, he'd go out
and gorged himself on human blood.

730
01:53:49,310 --> 01:53:51,269
I kept his secrets...

731
01:53:51,270 --> 01:53:52,979
cleaned up the mess.

732
01:53:53,490 --> 01:53:55,439
But it was he...

733
01:53:55,440 --> 01:54:00,869
who crept room to room
dispatching everyone close to your heart.

734
01:54:01,790 --> 01:54:03,909
But when he got to you,

735
01:54:04,160 --> 01:54:08,039
he just couldn't bear the thought
of draining you dry.

736
01:54:08,040 --> 01:54:13,299
You, who reminded him so much
of his precious Sonja...

737
01:54:14,210 --> 01:54:18,299
the daughter he condemned to death.

738
01:54:18,760 --> 01:54:19,839
Lies.

739
01:54:19,840 --> 01:54:21,889
Believe what you want.

740
01:54:22,850 --> 01:54:24,519
Now come on.

741
01:54:24,520 --> 01:54:26,979
Your place is by my side.

742
01:54:32,190 --> 01:54:33,190
[ COCKS GUN ]

743
01:54:34,030 --> 01:54:35,989
So be it.

744
01:55:05,060 --> 01:55:06,349
Bite him!

745
01:55:09,900 --> 01:55:12,099
[ MAN ] Half-Vampire...

746
01:55:12,100 --> 01:55:14,069
half-Lycan...

747
01:55:14,070 --> 01:55:17,109
but stronger than both.

748
01:55:42,720 --> 01:55:45,219
What the hell are you doing?

749
01:55:46,010 --> 01:55:48,469
You may have killed me...

750
01:55:49,270 --> 01:55:50,519
cousin.

751
01:55:50,520 --> 01:55:52,689
But my will...

752
01:55:52,690 --> 01:55:55,439
is done regardless.

753
01:56:35,610 --> 01:56:37,479
Where is he?

754
01:56:38,570 --> 01:56:39,819
Where's Kraven?

755
01:57:01,170 --> 01:57:03,509
Forgive me, my child.

756
01:57:04,840 --> 01:57:06,719
It wasn't the Lycans.

757
01:57:08,850 --> 01:57:10,679
It was you.

758
01:57:17,560 --> 01:57:19,519
Leave us.

759
01:57:38,500 --> 01:57:43,379
How could you bear my trust
knowing that you'd killed my family?

760
01:57:44,550 --> 01:57:46,259
Yes.

761
01:57:46,890 --> 01:57:48,719
I have taken from you.

762
01:57:50,350 --> 01:57:53,429
But I have given so much more.

763
01:57:54,390 --> 01:57:59,559
Is it not a fair trade, the life I have
granted you? The gift of immortality?

764
01:57:59,770 --> 01:58:02,529
And the life of your daughter?

765
01:58:02,860 --> 01:58:05,279
Your own flesh and blood?

766
01:58:26,300 --> 01:58:29,009
I loved my daughter!

767
01:58:31,300 --> 01:58:36,559
But the abomination growing in her womb
was a betrayal of me and of the coven!

768
01:58:41,730 --> 01:58:49,149
I did what was necessary to protect the
species, as I am forced to do yet again.

769
01:58:53,200 --> 01:58:54,200
No!

770
02:01:31,940 --> 02:01:33,279
[ROARS]

771
02:01:47,630 --> 02:01:49,249
Time to die.

772
02:03:21,090 --> 02:03:22,719
[ LYCAN GROWLS ]

773
02:05:09,160 --> 02:05:11,869
[ SELENE ]
Though I cannot predict the future,

774
02:05:11,870 --> 02:05:15,319
the consequences of this night
will reverberate through the halls

775
02:05:15,320 --> 02:05:18,919
of both great covens
for many years to come.

776
02:05:20,380 --> 02:05:23,169
Two Vampire elders have been slain,

777
02:05:23,170 --> 02:05:25,589
one by my own hand.

778
02:05:27,350 --> 02:05:31,179
Soon, Marcus will take the throne.

779
02:05:32,430 --> 02:05:37,019
And a tide of anger and retribution
will spill out into the night.

780
02:05:38,770 --> 02:05:41,439
Differences will be set aside.

781
02:05:42,030 --> 02:05:44,359
Allegiances will be made.

782
02:05:44,900 --> 02:05:46,489
And soon...

783
02:05:46,490 --> 02:05:49,319
I will become the hunted.

